When youre troubleshooting a system that wont boot, which of the following lines can beplaced on the kernel command line in order to invoke a debugging shell?
A)  debug,shell
B)  systemd.debug- shell=1
C)  shell=debug
D)  emerg=debug
B
B. Using systemd.debug- shell=1 on the kernel command line results in a debugshell being made available early in the boot process. The other options are not valid forthis purpose.
